# t5-small-finetuned-wikisql-with-cols

This model is a fine-tuned version of [t5-small](https://huggingface.co/t5-small) on the wikisql dataset using a (slightly modified) training script by [Manuel Romero](https://huggingface.co/mrm8488).
It achieves the following results on the evaluation set:
- Loss: 0.0282
- Rouge2 Precision: 0.9172
- Rouge2 Recall: 0.819
- Rouge2 Fmeasure: 0.8578
